  "summary": "Malicious code in streamvault (npm)",
  "details": "Streamvault@1.0.1 is a trojan logging library that depends on byteboxlab, which contains an RCE downloader. Upon loading the module, it fetches a second-stage payload from hxxps://axioshealthcheck[.]vercel[.]app/debugCheck?id=\u003cDEBUG_value\u003e via HTTPS POST. The response contains a base64-encoded JavaScript payload that is decoded and executed via new Function(code)(require), giving the attacker arbitrary code execution on the installed system. The downloader retries up to 10 times within a 60-second window. The package impersonates a real developer to appear legitimate.",
